@node Game



                                  The Game

 You know this Game under the Name Black Jack, but its only with  32  Cards.
 Thats  makes  it faster and its realy the german Way to play this Game. The
 missing Cards are from 2 to 6. You got only the Cards from 7  to  the  Ace.
 For People they never play it befor here the Rules:
 You must come very closed to the Amount of 21 Points. If you  or  the  Bank
 (thats the Computer) mean its enough and take no more Cards, then the other
 one must try to reach more Points (but not more then 21 !).
 But remember, if you take no more Cards you got no second Chance to reach
 21, because you have finished the Game on this Way.
 The Bank win, if the Points are the same (as example you  got  18  and  the
 Bank to). So you must get every Time more than the Bank.
 Points over 21 lose.
 There is only one Exception: When the Game starts and the first 2 Cards are
 2 Aces. Thats called Fire. The Person with Fire is the Winner.
 For one Card more press with the left Mousebutton on the Cardstuck.
 Do you wish no more Cards, then you press on "Ready !".
 If you wanne quit, then you must press the right Mousebutton and  klick  in
 the Menu the Button "Quit".
 And now how much Points is which Card.

                                @{" The Cards " link Cards}
