@node Cards



                                  The Cards

                             Points of the Cards

                                     7=7
                                     8=8
                                     9=9
                                    10=10
                                     J=2
                                     Q=3
                                     K=4
          Ace=11 or by more then 2 Cards and more then 11 Points =1
